	<h1 class="title">听说芭比想认真和你的孩子交朋友，是美梦成真还是细思略恐？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">James Vlahos</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-09-21 10:22:59 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15158/medium/15158.jpg?1442735173" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="15158" data-title="《听说芭比想认真和你的孩子交朋友，是美梦成真还是细思略恐？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/15158/medium/15158.jpg?1442735173" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/15158.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
